result.name: PizzaExpress Kornhill Plaza

reviews.text:
Doesn't have to wait for long time before getting a table for two.

There are a wide range of choices of starters, pizza, and pasta. 

One of the starters was extremely well baked.( "small bun baked with cheese" maybe? I have forgotten the name of the dish hahaha)

Really great restaurant for party or family size.

Dessert however was a disappointment for me. The lava cake looks great but it was just undercooked, so it was like drinking condensed chocolate milk; a bit too heavy for me.
Service was good. Great dinner menu offer. Food was really nice.
Has many options and consistent quality in all the stores. Nice ambience.

Great Pizza and food.

We enjoy the kid menu a lot with attractive price!

Please be patient as they are always busy, need to wait a bit long time for food.
There was nothing wrong with eating experience, good service, clean and food came out without any problems. Overall nice, relaxed location with alot windows.
